name: Routing-home-2
tagline: work for 2nd landing page for that routing thing
body:
## 2nd landing page for that routing thing.
The routing thing needs a new landing page and this space will be used for shared development and issue tracking and listing

This page is to ultimately be incorporated into the application site as it's default landing page.  For that a number of changes will need to be made to support it's new location.  Isolated development away from the eventual location means pathing for images, css, and included libraries will need to be edited as part of the deployment.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
